description: Welcome to 13 Telegraph Street.  An 1135 S/F Penthouse Condo with 2 spacious bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms w/ in-unit laundry.  Vaulted ceilings on the top floor, open kitchen, dining, and living area w/ fireplace - perfect for relaxing or entertaining.  Sky lights provide increased natural light to increase the open living feel and look.  Both large bedrooms have ample closet space and are divided by a bathroom for maximum privacy.  Relax on a deck off the main bedroom or use the deck off the kitchen and utilize the electric awning for peaceful enjoyment.   ***Location*** Close to all modes of public transportation, minutes to the Seaport, Downtown, and the Back Bay and highways. Just a quick walk to Historic Dorchester Heights / Thomas Park or Beaches nearby.  Just blocks from local vibrant restaurants, shops, parks, and all things South Boston.  Priced for upgrades..., stop by the OH Saturday 11-1 and Sunday 12-2..., great rental alternative and ownership opportunity!
